---
import { Button } from "flowbite-react";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base.astro";
import Navigationbar from '../components/navbar';
import {
  TextRevealCard,
  TextRevealCardDescription,
  TextRevealCardTitle,
} from "@/components/ui/text-reveal-card";
---
<BaseLayout title={"Vision"} description={"The vision of the DAccelerator for the next generation of entrepreneurs, artists, scientists and creators"}>
    <Navigationbar client:load/>
    <main class='w-[80%] flex flex-col gap-8 justify-center items-center mt-8 md:mt-24'>
        <div>
            <h1 class="my-4 md:text-8xl text-4xl font-black text-center text-primary">Vision</h1>
        <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center items-center">
            <TextRevealCard
        text="Accelerator &nbsp&nbsp for &nbsp&nbsp Startups"
        revealText="DAccelerator for DeStartups" client:load
            ></TextRevealCard>
        </div>
            <div class="my-6 p-8 border-double border-4 border-primary">
                <p class="text-center text-lg md:text-xl mx-auto">
                    <b>DAccelerator: Empowering Global Entrepreneurship</b>
                    <br/><br/>
                    At Start Head, we envision a future where entrepreneurship knows no boundaries. DAccelerator, our decentralized accelerator, is a revolutionary concept born from the belief that innovation should serve the entire world, not just a specific location. In traditional business landscapes, geography often limits ambition, but in the digital realm, there are no borders. 
                    
                    Sadly, skepticism around blockchain and Web3 technologies has caused many to lose trust, viewing these innovations as scams. But the truth is, it’s not about <b>who</b> you are, it's about the value you create for the ecosystem. Regardless of where you come from, anyone who contributes meaningfully can benefit from the decentralized economy. 
                    
                    We aim to help people accelerate their ideas and create solutions that serve humanity. Global challenges like cancer don’t belong to Jakarta, Dubai, or Tashkent alone—they belong to all of us. Through decentralized startups, we believe the world's most pressing problems can be tackled by harnessing the power of collective innovation.
                    
                    Join us, and let's build a future without boundaries, where technology empowers everyone to create for the greater good.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/HADXy8Je" target="_blank"><Button outline color="gray"><span class="flex items-center fa-brands fa-discord pr-2"></span><span>Join Discord Channel</span></Button></a>
        <p class='text-center mx-auto'>StartHead©, All rights Reserved.</p>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>